Looking up map in JSTL - integer vs long

This page demonstrates how JSTL maps interact with different types used for keys in a map. Specifically the issue relates to autoboxing by java using map.put(1, MyValue) and attempting to display it as ${myMap[1]} The map myMap consists of four entries with different keys: A String, an Integer, a Long and an entry put there by AutoBoxing Java 5 feature. 1> entry items=${myMap} varStatus=status>
